init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I could see my furry face on the screen and immediately recognized my nose and mouth, but I had no idea how they would get away with showing a

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I was very surprised to see that I was a cat, but I also thought that it made perfect sense.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The movie went on to show me that I had been a cat for many years and had lived a happy, complete life.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I had a wonderful, loving relationship with this woman and she treated me very well.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Her health was starting to fail, and she knew that her days were numbered.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: She told me that she wanted to take care of one final thing before she died.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "She is very nice, and she will make sure you are taken care of.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As she was dying, she told me to be a good boy and that she would always take care of me.
